Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.90,0:00:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.73,0:00:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.44,0:00:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.42,0:00:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.19,0:00:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.90,0:00:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.67,0:00:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.04,0:00:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.15,0:01:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.25,0:01:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.75,0:01:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.19,0:01:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.86,0:01:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.23,0:01:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.77,0:01:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.20,0:01:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,原來妳是個寡婦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.77,0:01:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請忘記死掉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我交往吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.34,0:02:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.11,0:02:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道我…難道我就不行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.38,0:02:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的要說的話,的確不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.09,0:02:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,響子,飯還沒好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.62,0:02:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.56,0:02:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你終於出現了,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.07,0:02:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,不可以\N那個人已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.14,0:02:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的丈夫已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.84,0:02:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎沒有死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.21,0:02:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎比你好太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是能力或肚量都比你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.75,0:02:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長相也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.99,0:02:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?我很美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.42,0:02:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.99,0:02:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.23,0:03:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#07 五代煩惱不已!響子喜歡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.55,0:03:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.29,0:03:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過這個夢也太恐怖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.56,0:03:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一之瀨太太,真是的\N討厭,妳又來跟我提那件事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.40,0:03:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這麼說,至少看看照片嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位是K大畢業的\N在貿易公司上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.83,0:03:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長得一表人才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.54,0:03:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外這個家世好得不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.24,0:03:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我個人比較喜歡這個帥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.21,0:03:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次我已經跟妳說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有再婚的打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.75,0:03:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話不要說得這麼硬嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.85,0:03:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看看照片有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.89,0:03:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂,我這樣就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.49,0:04:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳想為你老公守寡,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.73,0:04:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不流行這個了\N更何況妳這麼年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了一個死去的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎還沒有死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.21,0:04:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.55,0:04:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是你,五代!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.05,0:04:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.69,0:04:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經中午了,怎麼還不去上學?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.63,0:04:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想說下午再去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.40,0:04:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在等她晒完內褲吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.07,0:04:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別…別開玩笑了!我哪有!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.37,0:04:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,竟然被看穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法,還是上課去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.23,0:05:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.70,0:05:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣好嗎?已經中午了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦,不要急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.78,0:05:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,惣一郎,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.62,0:05:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.62,0:05:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這是一條狗耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.06,0:05:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狗又怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.70,0:05:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳…妳還是覺得狗比較好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.44,0:05:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了,停課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.88,0:06:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又停課了啊\N那個教授是不是快掛了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.32,0:06:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨,五代,要不要去喝杯咖啡?\N反正停課不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.06,0:06:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,我是為了什麼來的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.76,0:06:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝咖啡,你要請客嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是白痴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.53,0:06:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪會被甩一巴掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.34,0:06:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般怎麼會說這種話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.47,0:06:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不小心說溜嘴的\N因為那個夢實在太強烈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.61,0:06:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會作那種夢,你本身就有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.74,0:06:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是一種心結吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.52,0:06:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我總覺得在管理員的背後\N看到她死去的老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.06,0:06:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是個怎麼樣的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.06,0:06:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長得什麼樣子?\N什麼樣的聲音?什麼樣的個性?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.23,0:06:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿腦子想得都是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.40,0:07:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看那個管理員對他那麼癡迷\N那個男的一定很有魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是感覺好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.94,0:07:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管心愛的人死了\N對他的愛也終生不渝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種想法不健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?這樣很浪漫不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.75,0:07:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們一定發過誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.96,0:07:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管肉體分開了\N兩顆心也會永遠在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.46,0:07:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!絕對不行!\N一定要把他忘了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.86,0:07:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然再婚的話\N彼此都會不幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在發什麼飆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是你要跟她再婚\N那就另當別論…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.31,0:07:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你是這麼打算的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.01,0:07:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一杯熱咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.89,0:07:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個人根本靠不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.79,0:07:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我眼裡你就已經是這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.23,0:07:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況年紀大的女人\N就更不用說了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.06,0:07:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我畢業了以後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.03,0:08:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候你幾歲了?\N管理員的年齡也會自動增加的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.94,0:08:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不會變老的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.31,0:08:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,讓你請客了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝招待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.99,0:08:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結婚的事\N等你有了穩定的工作再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.36,0:08:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前,學分不要被當掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,一點都不好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.83,0:08:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著吧,我也會有作為的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,妳在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.95,0:08:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公,對不起\N因為我還是改不了以前的習慣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.22,0:08:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經不是以前的五代了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.49,0:08:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大學第一名畢業\N現在賺的錢比別人還多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.76,0:09:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是要妳把這種事\N交給女傭做就好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.84,0:09:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳什麼都不用擔心\N在我的懷裡休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是個可靠的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.21,0:09:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人不要緊吧…\N他在幹什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚也只能吃這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去找個打工的工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.87,0:09:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隔壁鎮上的阪之湯澡堂\N在徵求兼職人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.74,0:09:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時薪560圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.21,0:09:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷,我說多少次了\N要進來請從門口敲門進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.54,0:09:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只錄取一名,動作要快喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.38,0:09:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我要去澡堂打工?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.92,0:10:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐在櫃台可以看見女人洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.83,0:10:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.96,0:10:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,到時候\N請你也要讓我偷窺一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.83,0:10:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是學生來打工\N他們會馬上讓我坐櫃台嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.10,0:10:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就要看交涉手腕囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.20,0:10:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情會有這麼順利嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要死皮賴臉地爭取…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.18,0:10:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷,請你不要太過份\N這是我的晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.95,0:10:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎以前不是\N這麼小氣的人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.73,0:10:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你見過惣一郎嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.57,0:10:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是個沒有缺點的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.94,0:11:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長相英俊,像是酷一點的玉三郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.61,0:11:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說話時意志堅強且溫和沈穩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.12,0:11:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他向管理員求婚那一幕\N才是驚心動魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.55,0:11:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然抱住她\N用熱吻傳達愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.46,0:11:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然是在他們初次見面的第二天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.94,0:11:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從以前就一直想像著\N他是這樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.55,0:11:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真想見他一面\N看他是不是如我想像的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你的泡麵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.45,0:11:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要偷窺喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦,過來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.82,0:12:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,你看\N繡球花開得好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,妳看這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.83,0:12:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,笑一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.52,0:12:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!要請五代當家教?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.87,0:13:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要請五代啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.38,0:13:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,郁子今年也要上國中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.15,0:13:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想說給她請個家教比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家商量的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.78,0:13:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代是個好青年\N而且郁子也很喜歡他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,妳覺得呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺,換我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.26,0:13:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下喔,郁子要跟妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子嬸嬸,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.37,0:13:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,郁子,我是這麼覺得啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.57,0:13:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唸書唸得開心當然是最好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.11,0:13:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要拿到好成績的話\N找個適合的人教比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.81,0:13:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要大哥哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.71,0:13:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要大哥哥!我要大哥哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.42,0:13:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳也聽到了\N妳可不可以先幫忙問問看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,好,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.54,0:14:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要鬧了,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.40,0:14:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算敲門進來,我也沒有泡麵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.17,0:14:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼嘛,臉皮比城牆還厚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.21,0:14:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家教?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.72,0:14:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不願意的話\N儘管拒絕沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.19,0:14:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.53,0:14:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我非常樂意接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.76,0:14:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.17,0:14:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是管理員特地幫我推薦的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼可能拒絕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼都沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠得到妳的信任\N我非常高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.91,0:14:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請儘管仰賴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.85,0:15:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,要請我當家教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我媽媽在找妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.62,0:15:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.79,0:15:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別看我這樣,我是唸教育系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.43,0:15:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對小孩子的教育很有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來就很喜歡小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撇開這些不談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能幫上管理員的忙\N我什麼都願意做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.90,0:15:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之,如果妳不嫌棄我的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.55,0:15:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,數學問題集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,橡皮擦兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,英文課本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.32,0:15:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鉛筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.42,0:15:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有預防萬一所準備的參考書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.36,0:15:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.26,0:15:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.87,0:15:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.40,0:15:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個拿給我家裡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,點心,當作見面禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.01,0:15:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下,你的釦子沒扣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要好好問候人家喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.22,0:16:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好教喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.63,0:16:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.56,0:16:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直像個照顧他的太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是有趣的一對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.01,0:16:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.64,0:16:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都看到了,從頭到尾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.87,0:16:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過妳也真是大膽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.78,0:16:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然請他當家教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.81,0:16:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的姪女是不是打算放棄\N今後的人生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不需要說得這麼難聽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.79,0:16:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞧妳現在擔心的樣子\N明明就不信任他,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.62,0:16:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒這回事…我只是覺得\N那個人不太靠得住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.50,0:16:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.87,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越來越像有那麼回事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.27,0:17:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.47,0:17:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜…拜託,你們到底想說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.84,0:17:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然有了話題可聊,來喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.48,0:17:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只有茶而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.64,0:17:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.36,0:17:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.06,0:17:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.96,0:17:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥,快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.96,0:17:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,你來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.06,0:17:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.00,0:17:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,郁子,要叫人家老師才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是郁子的母親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.97,0:17:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次真的是麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.21,0:17:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裡,別這麼說\N請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.88,0:17:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這孩子很任性\N不聽話的話,請儘管罵她沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會乖乖地聽話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看這孩子就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事經常聽到不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.92,0:17:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太太跟家教偷情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.19,0:17:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不會呢\N我大嫂不是那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.93,0:18:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過男人耐不住的時候\N會霸王硬上弓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.13,0:18:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊對啊,男人是沒有節操的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以我大嫂的力氣來說\N一定打得贏他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.50,0:18:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一來要擔心的\N就是妳的姪女了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.14,0:18:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要開這種玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.84,0:18:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,郁子才12歲而已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的小孩發育得都很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.61,0:18:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且五代意志薄弱\N很容易控制不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.82,0:18:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,一個恍神就出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.72,0:18:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要再說了\N我的胸口變得好難受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.22,0:18:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真的發生這種事\N我真的是難辭其咎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.66,0:18:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老天爺,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.06,0:18:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千萬不要讓這種恐怖的事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戲弄她真的很好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為她會當真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.27,0:18:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是BE動詞,懂了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼主詞是T0M的時候呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.38,0:18:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師,你有心上人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以講跟課業無關的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.95,0:18:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把話題閃開,一定是有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閃開話題的人是妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.89,0:18:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又轉移話題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.12,0:19:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請喝茶…\N所以,這裡要用X乘以2的公式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.80,0:19:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝,不用客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,郁子有沒有認真在學?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然有囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.24,0:19:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼老師,請你多費心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.71,0:19:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.24,0:19:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以讓老師為難喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.61,0:19:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休息時間,我們來玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,累死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.42,0:19:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,我拿相簿給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼會碰上這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.63,0:19:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看,這張這張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.89,0:19:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是七五三節慶的時候\N去明治神宮照的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.83,0:19:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好,真是可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.80,0:19:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(和惣一郎叔叔)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.77,0:19:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一張?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.57,0:19:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我穿和服很好看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.34,0:19:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…妳穿和服很好看\N然後啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.38,0:19:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝,接下來是學藝會的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.02,0:20:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是,我是說下面這張照片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.29,0:20:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一張?這張照片很無聊耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臉的部分被撕掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.32,0:20:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我惡作劇撕掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.23,0:20:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳叔叔一定長得很帥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不帥啊,反而他有點怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.63,0:20:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看這張,我是女主角\N我演的是輝夜公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.64,0:20:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有在看嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有啊,好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.01,0:20:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,接下來是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.31,0:20:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,響子嬸嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.54,0:20:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(和新嬸嬸)\N這是她剛嫁過來的時候拍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.15,0:20:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是惣一郎叔叔幫我們拍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.82,0:20:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.47,0:20:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留你到這麼晚,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.91,0:20:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後也請你多費心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.94,0:20:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不能辭職喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.58,0:21:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.55,0:21:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.96,0:21:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然要帶小孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.89,0:21:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都這麼晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.76,0:21:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他差不多該回來了才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.83,0:21:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟在做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.70,0:21:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.01,0:21:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.05,0:22:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種無憂無慮的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.06,0:22:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是完全信賴著男人的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.79,0:22:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從來沒有見過她那種笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.65,0:22:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.65,0:22:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.78,0:22:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事,倒是家教的情形如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.96,0:23:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕,是不是發生了\N什麼不好的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.97,0:23:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個\N她總是露出擔心的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.11,0:23:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,笑一笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.45,0:23:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,笑容最美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.32,0:23:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.63,0:23:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他故意裝得很開朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.63,0:23:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是出了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.04,0:23:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我絕對不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.45,0:23:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要這樣,五代,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.92,0:23:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算喝醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.22,0:23:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不會原諒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.12,0:23:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.09,0:24:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『五代激情吶喊\N該做的時候還是要做!』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.89,0:24:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛不是用吶喊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.86,0:24:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛是很高貴的東西\N是存放於心裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.45,0:24:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何妳能如此若無其事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.76,0:24:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光只是眨個眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.90,0:24:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能讓我悸動不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.80,0:24:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使我身陷險境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.11,0:24:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明已經可以相愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.75,0:25:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偏偏時機還不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.12,0:25:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我快要忍受不了\N快要變成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.67,0:25:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是痛苦的折磨

